description: The wey is much less occupied here, its only tenant being a small stone cottage set far back from the street.  The cottage's diamond-paned glaesine windows glow with a warm amber hue in the dark night.  Columbine covers the ironwork fence surrounding the cottage, its blooms barely visible in the quicksilver moonlight.

The wey is much less occupied here, its only tenant being a small stone cottage set far back from the street.  Columbine covers the ironwork fence surrounding the cottage, its deep pink blooms nodding drowsily in the sunlight.

The wey is barely built up along this stretch, its only tenant being a small stone house set far back from the street.  Columbine covers the ironwork fence surrounding the building, its white blooms open wide to receive the evening.  Meandering away, a cobbled walk is marked with lit silver lanterns.

title: [Ta'Illistim, Sylvar Wey]
